        <defName>Zd_DiligenceArm</defName>
        <label>diligence arm</label>
        <labelNoun>an diligence arm</labelNoun>
        <description>An installed diligence arm. It's strong enough to crush a thick hardwood branch
            in its hand, and precise enough to write a sonnet on a grain of rice. It looks and feels
